g.text: Tagline font: Over the Rainbow Regular
Yellow (#FEFF00) is THE accent - use sparingly (max 10% of composition)
Black (#000000) is default background - dark mode is the brand
Shark (#1A1A1E) for cards and elevated surfaces
Bombay (#B3B9C0) for circuit brain and secondary text
NEVER use multiple accent colors - yellow is it
NEVER use gradients or color fades
Use ONLY for tagline "bookmarks for your brain!"
ALWAYS in yellow (#FEFF00), NEVER for any other text
Font: Lato Black (or similar bold sans-serif)
Line art style, geometric, 2px stroke weight
Clear Space: Height of bookmark flag on all sides
NOT a note app. NOT a voice memo app.
A cognitive capture tool built for speed, not organization.
"Capture ideas at the speed of life"
Thoughtmarks Brand Style Guide v2.0 | thoughtmarks.app
